1
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:50,240
Uncle.

2
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,400
How many times have I told you?

3
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:55,440
All you know is fighting and killing.

4
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,280
Put the gun down.

5
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:01,200
Put the gun down.

6
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:10,880
My nephew's young and hotheaded.

7
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,480
He's got a temper.

8
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:13,680
Dawa.

9
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,800
Apologize to the two bosses

10
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:17,040
right now.

11
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,000
I'm sorry.

12
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:22,680
That's not very sincere.

13
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,040
I'm sorry.

14
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,320
I was too impulsive just now.

15
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:30,720
Please forgive me.

16
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,880
That's a better attitude.

17
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:35,400
Now that's more like it.

18
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,280
Come on.

19
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:37,960
Do me a small favor.

20
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,120
Let's just let this

21
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,640
slide this time.

22
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:46,640
Hong Ye has spoken.

23
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,080
You're forgiven.

24
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,240
Hong Ye.

25
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,120
Where's Lao Zhang?

26
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,040
Lao Zhang?

27
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,120
Lao Zhang is...

28
00:01:59,040 --> 00:01:59,960
Dr. Zhang.

29
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,280
Don't worry.

30
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:02,840
Right now,

31
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,240
he's at my place having tea.

32
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,880
I've got nothing but good tea.

33
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,560
Wanna see him?

34
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:09,920
Come.

35
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:14,880
Lao Zhang.

36
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,880
How are you?

37
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:16,960
I'm fine.

38
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,280
Of course I'm fine.

39
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,640
Hong Ye's been very hospitable.

40
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,960
He invited me here specially

41
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,240
to talk about working together.

42
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,320
I emailed you guys.

43
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,640
We didn't get it.

44
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,040
We got it.

45
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,240
What did Hong Ye invite you for?

46
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,960
Hong Ye's got great vision.

47
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:36,400
He wants a long-term partnership with us.

48
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,480
To a great partnership.

49
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,600
To a great partnership.

50
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,600
As for me,

51
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:53,360
I want to work with your company.

52
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,640
I know President Shen

53
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,880
has been making high-end chips.

54
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,760
And I happen to need them too.

55
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,160
High-end chips.

56
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,600
No problem.

57
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,360
But Lao Zhang

58
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,880
is our company's chief scientist.

59
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,680
If you want the chips,

60
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,520
he has to come back first.

61
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,680
But time waits for no one.

62
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,160
I hope to get your answer

63
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,080
by tomorrow.

64
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,000
Otherwise, what if Dr. Zhang

65
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,280
ends up liking it at my place?

66
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,440
I'll wait for your answer tomorrow.

67
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,520
Let's go.

68
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:32,440
Uncle.

69
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,520
I don't get it.

70
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,280
Why work with her?

71
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,680
Why not just kidnap her and be done?

72
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,520
Idiot.

73
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,520
How many times have I told you,

74
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,520
use your brain.

75
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,280
Do you know what I want?

76
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:46,240
I want their chips.

77
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:50,520
Chips are used to make high-tech weapons.

78
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:52,840
Once we get high-tech weapons,

79
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:55,160
beyond Dongba,

80
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:56,600
in all of Sanjiepo,

81
00:03:57,520 --> 00:04:00,000
who would dare stand against us?

82
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,280
Use your head.

83
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,760
Go.

84
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,960
Hong Ye grabbed Dr. Zhang to threaten you

85
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,880
so he can get the chips

86
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,040
to make high-tech weapons.

87
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:18,360
Wars from now on will be different.

88
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,720
No more soldiers charging the front lines.

89
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,400
From now on,

90
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,600
it'll be robots

91
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,200
and smart drone warfare.

92
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,640
So the demand for high-tech chips is high.

93
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,480
So for now,

94
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,080
we need to stall Hong Ye,

95
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,920
and figure out a way to save Dr. Zhang.

96
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:38,680
I'm really sorry.

97
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,920
I didn't deliver on what I promised.

98
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,560
And I dragged you into all this.

99
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,680
Don't worry.

100
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,960
As long as I'm still standing,

101
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,760
no one's gonna hurt you.

102
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,520
Hello, Hong Ye.

103
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,160
Working together's fine.

104
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,120
President Shen is a smart woman.

105
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,120
I believe

106
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,520
President Shen would see reason.

107
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,080
But you also know

108
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,960
this deal is highly profitable.

109
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:20,800
Our company happens to need massive funding

110
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,840
for R&D and production.

111
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,600
So once the money comes in,

112
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:25,000
I want a 50-50 split.

113
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,560
Looks like President Shen knows

114
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,840
how much risk is involved in this business.

115
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,640
A 70-30 split.

116
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:31,880
You get 30 at most.

117
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:35,880
Fine.

118
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,640
But the chips

119
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:39,440
are under global scrutiny right now.

120
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,360
We can't afford any mistakes.

121
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:44,120
So I need time to clear the channels

122
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,320
before we can ship the chips.

123
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,760
Time's not a problem.

124
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:49,320
But I need to see first

125
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:51,240
who's in charge of the shipment.

126
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:52,480
Okay.

127
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,240
I'll arrange for him to come over ASAP.

128
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:54,720
Okay.

129
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:57,760
Uncle, you're really splitting with her?

130
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,200
That woman is sharp.

131
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,840
She figured out our goal right away.

132
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,360
So what if she did?

133
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,320
This is Dongba.

134
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:09,120
She's gotta play by our rules.

135
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,480
What the hell do you know?

136
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,920
I'm not just after their chips.

137
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:14,920
What I want more is

138
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:17,200
their channels for shipping the chips.

139
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,240
We

140
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,360
use huge profits first

141
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,440
to reel her in.

142
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,280
Once the deal's done,

143
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,640
then

144
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,040
we call the shots.

145
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,600
Bro Xingchen.

146
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,400
Ma Liu.

147
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,080
You just got here, or you're leaving?

148
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,760
I'm going upstairs to grab something.

149
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,800
All right.

150
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,960
Do you know anyone reliable around here

151
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,640
who can pose as a distributor?

152
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,640
Hong Ye is sly as a fox.

153
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,440
Anyone we find in Dongba

154
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,080
won't be able to fool him.

155
00:06:59,160 --> 00:06:59,880
How about this.

156
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,560
If we're putting on a show, we go all in.

157
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:02,880
Find someone from back home,

158
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,760
and bring them over.

159
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,000
Bro.

160
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:25,280
Send someone reliable on a trip to Dongba.

161
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,160
I need someone to pose as a distributor.

162
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,400
Sis!

163
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:44,640
Something's wrong!

164
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,480
Shen Xingyu's teaming up with Hong Ye.

165
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,600
Isn't Shen Xingyu's a tech company?

166
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,920
What are they teaming up on?

167
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,640
High-tech weapons.

168
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,200
Is that confirmed?

169
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,360
One hundred percent.

170
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,240
Shen Xingyu's sending people to Dongba right now.

171
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,440
What do we do?

172
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,000
Send people to stop them, now.

173
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,040
We can't let them work together.

174
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,040
Okay, okay.

175
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,480
They're already late.

176
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:11,880
Why aren't they here yet?

177
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,520
The rule of thumb in Dongba:

178
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,800
when things are unusual, something's fishy.

179
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,040
Looks like we

180
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,280
need a backup plan now.

181
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,440
Something must've happened.

182
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,680
President Shen.

183
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,560
President Shen!

184
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,160
Ma Liu.

185
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,000
What are you doing here?

186
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:33,840
What happened to you?

187
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,680
Lao Tian and I were on our way to find you.

188
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:38,040
The moment we stepped out, we got jumped.

189
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:40,040
Lao Tian's still laid up in the hospital.

190
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:42,520
Doc says he won't wake up for four or five days.

191
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:44,080
A woman called Sis Fei

192
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,000
told me to pass a message to you.

193
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:48,680
She said Dongba needs "balance."

194
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:50,120
And she said if certain things happen,

195
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:52,120
you won't be able to handle the fallout.

196
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:03,240
President Shen...

197
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:06,200
I saw Wu Di's ghost.

198
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:08,600
He's sitting right here.

199
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:12,320
If only you were still alive, Bro Wu Di.

200
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,560
Then I wouldn't have been beaten up like this.

201
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,480
Bro Wu Di...

202
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:20,160
I'm not used to men being this close to me.

203
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:22,440
He's not Zhao Wu Di.

204
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,280
They just look alike.

205
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,200
Alright.

206
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:29,640
Back to business.

207
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,800
Why's Sis Fei stirring things up?

208
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:35,200
If we team up with Hong Ye on arms right now,

209
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:36,440
then Sis Fei

210
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,880
will lose her foothold.

211
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,840
Of course she won't just sit back.

212
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,440
I won't let a few of her words

213
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:44,800
intimidate me.

214
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:45,800
Enough.

215
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,520
With Sis Fei,

216
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,840
we'll send someone to explain later.

217
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,640
Our top priority right now is

218
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,160
to find someone to pose as the distributor.

219
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:03,000
If it's someone who's been laying low

220
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:04,800
in Dongba, wouldn't it seem

221
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,720
more convincing to Hong Ye?

222
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,960
Me?

223
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:18,840
You've gotta be kidding.

224
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,120
Hong Ye and Dawa have both seen me.

225
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,760
You can do it.

226
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,120
You look so much like Bro Wu Di.

227
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,240
You could pretend to be him.

228
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,600
Be President Shen's temporary husband.

229
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:30,000
Everyone here knows I'm a waiter.

230
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,360
They won't buy it.

231
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,120
That's why we need

232
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:36,120
to spin a good story.

233
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:58,920
Miss Shen.

234
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,520
Hong Ye sent me to collect the debt.
